    • exportTables

      public void exportTables(CcddClassesComponent.FileEnvVar exportFile, List<CcddClassesDataTable.TableInfo> tableDefs, boolean includeBuildInformation, boolean replaceMacros, boolean includeVariablePaths, CcddVariableHandler variableHandler, String[] separators, String outputType, Object... extraInfo) throws JAXBException, MarshalException, CcddClassesDataTable.CCDDException, Exception
      Export the specified tables in XTCE XML format to the specified file
      Specified by:
      exportTables in interface CcddImportExportInterface
      Parameters:
      exportFile - Reference to the user-specified output file
      tableDefs - List of table definitions to convert
      includeBuildInformation - True to include the CCDD version, project, host, and user information
      replaceMacros - * Not used for XTCE export (all macros are expanded) * true to replace any embedded macros with their corresponding values
      includeVariablePaths - * Not used for XTCE export * true to include the variable path for each variable in a structure table, both in application format and using the user-defined separator characters
      variableHandler - * Not used for XTCE export * variable handler class reference; null if includeVariablePaths is false
      separators - * Not used for XTCE export * string array containing the variable path separator character(s), show/hide data types flag ('true' or 'false'), and data type/variable name separator character(s); null if includeVariablePaths is false
      extraInfo - [0] endianess (EndianType.BIG_ENDIAN or EndianType.LITTLE_ENDIAN)
      [1] are the telemetry and command headers big endian (true or false)
      [2] version attribute
      [3] validation status attribute
      [4] classification attribute
      outputType - String representing rather the output is going to a single file or multiple files. Should be "Single" or "Multiple"
      Throws:
      JAXBException - If an error occurs marshaling the project
      CcddClassesDataTable.CCDDException - If an error occurs executing an external (script) method
      Exception - If an unanticipated error occurs
      MarshalException

    • convertTablesToXTCE

      private void convertTablesToXTCE(List<CcddClassesDataTable.TableInfo> tableDefs, boolean includeBuildInformation, CcddConstants.EndianType endianess, boolean isHeaderBigEndian, String version, String validationStatus, String classification) throws CcddClassesDataTable.CCDDException
      Convert the project database contents to XTCE XML format
      Parameters:
      tableDefs - List of table definitions to convert
      includeBuildInformation - True to include the CCDD version, project, host, and user information
      endianess - EndianType.BIG_ENDIAN for big endian, EndianType.LITTLE_ENDIAN for little endian
      isHeaderBigEndian - True if the telemetry and command headers are always big endian (e.g., as with CCSDS)
      version - Version attribute
      validationStatus - Validation status attribute
      classification - Classification attribute
      Throws:
      CcddClassesDataTable.CCDDException - An error occurs converting the table(s) to XTCE
